cu.explanation_en: Setting ASN.1 verbosity to an unknown level will cause parsing errors in ASN.1 messages, leading to communication failures between network components.

du.explanation_en: Setting ASN.1 verbosity to an unknown level will cause parsing errors in ASN.1 messages, leading to communication failures between network components.
du.explanation_zh: 將 ASN.1 詳細程度設定為未知級別會導致 ASN.1 消息解析錯誤，導致網路元件間的通信失敗。
